{"tid":2144090,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方稱沙田發現可疑汽車 正了解有相片顯示警員舉槍","createTime":"2020-08-07T13:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T16:22:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a06c053f3e924328f824aa9543187cc0b3d24e94","tid":2144090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:15:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F126256&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6HyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=a1f3bf83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/126256</a><br />\n<br />\n警方表示，傍晚在港鐵顯徑站一段車公廟路，發現可疑汽車，追截期間私家車撞到一輛小巴和客貨車。對於網上流傳相片，一名警員舉槍指向私家車，警方表示仍在了解。沙田區區議員陳運通表示，下午約7時收到街坊求助，表示警員追截一輪灰色私家車，私家車撞向一輛小巴和客貨車後停下。警員要求車上的人下車但被拒，期間有警員拔槍。他又說，警方在車上搜出懷疑毒品。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-07 21:03:43"},{"pid":"868fa013fc9caaa2bf5a5661c8eeea8d63518deb","tid":2144090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd7305e9e7bc4e809b47bbfce678cab416aeac","tid":2144090,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e641fee56604af66d55ae02ad8c701aff11df5cd","tid":2144090,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset